<h3>Miscellaneous</h3>
<details>
  <summary>What do the colors mean?</summary>
  <p>Light blue: no blurbs; medium blue: 1-5 blurbs; green: 6-11 blurbs (minimum required for a full post); red: 11 blurbs; yellow: in editing process; white: published.</p>
</details>
<details>
